The following tables compare general and technical information for a number of '''[[file archiver]]s'''. Please see the individual products' articles for further information. They are neither all-inclusive nor are some entries necessarily up to date. Unless otherwise specified in the footnotes section, comparisons are based on the stable versions—''without'' add-ons, extensions or external programs.

