'''Notes:'''
# {{note|os-7zip-1}} A separate 64-bit [[Windows XP editions#Windows XP Professional x64 Edition|Windows x64 Edition]] version is also available.
# {{note|os-7zip-2}} The [[Unix-like]] system port is known as [[p7zip]]. p7zip also is provided by FreeDOS.
# {{note|os-7zip-3}} A [[Windows Mobile]] release (version 9.05-alpha onward) is available.
# {{note|os-7zip-4}} Aminet contains several solution for 7zip under both classic and newage Amiga OS. [http://aminet.net/search?query=7z]
# {{note|os-winace}} The programs for other platforms are called Unace, do not have the same [[GUI]], and can only perform decompression.
# {{note|os-winrar}} WinRAR is for Windows, RAR for other platforms.
# {{note|os-KGBArchiver}} This program also has a [[POSIX]] version available.
# {{note|os-infozip-1}} General [[Windows CE]] version.

